textobj-email
===

This is Vim plugin to provide text objects to select Email address.

I make following URL a reference.

[「PHP使いはもう正規表現をblogに書くな」と言わせないでくれ](http://blog.livedoor.jp/dankogai/archives/51189905.html)

Screenshot
---

Screenshot is under construction

Install
---

This plugin depends on [vim-textobj-user](http://github.com/kana/vim-textobj-user).

So you need to install [vim-textobj-user](http://github.com/kana/vim-textobj-user) together.

Usage
---

Default key mappings is `im` and `am` (operator mode).

`im` can use inner Email address as text object.

`am` equals to `im`.

For example `dim` to use delete inner Email address.

